description	"The Exile

^2Weaponry:
- The Exile's Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Fast Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Gun Defense   (2)
-- Saber Deflect (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Pull (3)
- Sense (1)
- Grip (2)

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

The human known as the Jedi Exile was a uniquely gifted Jedi Padawan who chose to disobey the orders of the Jedi High Council and aid the Galactic Republic in its struggle against the invading Mandalorian Neo-Crusaders during the Mandalorian Wars."